| `statement_timeout` | server | Postgres cancels a query exceeding this. Most reliable. |
| `query_timeout` | client | `pg` aborts the query locally (covers cases where the server never responds). |
| `idle_in_transaction_session_timeout` | server | Prevents a hung transaction from holding locks forever. |

